
Magn3t Software

Requirements:
-SWIG - for the python interface 
-Eigen library

Copile:
	-edit the makefile to point out the location of Python.h is. The default 
		location is /usr/local/include/python3.7m, or another version number
	-edit the makefile to point to the location of Eigen headers, the default is /usr/local/include/eigen3 

	-run:
		make
	
	At this point a shared library _magne3t.so is compiled and the python module magn3t.py. 
	These files should be kept in the same folder.





	
